theorem quotient_map_out_comp_out {C D E : homotopy_category V c} (f : «expr ⟶ » C D) (g : «expr ⟶ » D E) :
    (quotient V c).map («expr ≫ » (quot.out f) (quot.out g)) = «expr ≫ » f g := by

@[simp]
theorem quotient_map_out {C D : homotopy_category V c} (f : «expr ⟶ » C D) : (quotient V c).map f.out = f :=
  quot.out_eq _

homology_functor_map_factors:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ⟶ » -/
theorem homology_functor_map_factors (i : ι) {C D : homological_complex V c} (f : «expr ⟶ » C D) :
    (_root_.homology_functor V c i).map f = ((homology_functor V c i).map ((quotient V c).map f) : _) :=
  (category_theory.quotient.lift_map_functor_map _ (_root_.homology_functor V c i) _ f).symm
#align homology_functor_map_factors homology_functor_map_factors

eq_of_homotopy:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ⟶ » -/
theorem eq_of_homotopy {C D : homological_complex V c} (f g : «expr ⟶ » C D) (h : homotopy f g) :
    (quotient V c).map f = (quotient V c).map g :=
  category_theory.quotient.sound _ ⟨h⟩
#align eq_of_homotopy eq_of_homotopy
